                所谓“众里寻他千百度，蓦然回首，那人却在灯火阑珊处”仅仅是灵感吗？可灵感又是什么呢？有谁给过它顺理成章的解释吗？那么，依我看，灵感就是心魂的隔世接续。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37700517/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-05-03 17:12
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

    </div>

